info.x_cadence_note: Counts based on variable 'Epoch' in https://cdaweb.gsfc.nasa.gov/sp_phys/data/psp/sweap/spc/l3/l3i/2018/psp_swp_spc_l3i_20181031_v01.cdf. The most common cadence, 873820032 [ns] = PT0.87382S, occurred for 34.1889% of the 31835 timesteps.
info.contact: Justin C. Kasper @ University of Michigan
